PART 2: SEN ASSIGNMENT
Project: Student Result Management System
Project Description

A Student Result Management System is a Python-based application that allows users to:

Add students

Add scores

Calculate grades

Display student results

  SOFTWARE DEVELOPMENT LIFE CYCLE (SDLC)
1️ Planning Phase

Objective:
Build a system to manage student results easily.

Tools:

Python

GitHub

Users:

School staff / lecturers

2️ Requirements Analysis
Functional Requirements

Add student name

Add student score

Calculate grade

Display results

Non-Functional Requirements

Simple

Easy to use

Runs in terminal

3️ System Design
Program Structure
student_result_system/
│
├── main.py

Variables & Functions (NOMENCLATURE)
Name	Purpose
student_name	Stores student name
score	Stores score
calculate_grade()	Determines grade
display_result()	Shows output



